Its phone shopping time!

It’s been a while since Sanguis was in actual mun society so this place is mcfucking enigma to him, a arm shielding his eyes from the bright lights, “Ugh....is it always this ......damn bright everywhere?.”
"Im pretty sure its always been bright..." She chuckled a bit "Also....ive....never really been in a store like this before...." She did seem amazed at everything in the store
“Neither have I....well, not in a while....” he looks around the store, the amount of gadgets and technology starting to overwhelm him, “Well.....now what?..”
"Uhm....Lets....just pick out the tesseracts..." She hummed going over to the tesseract area and looking at them all
(Nya
“Y-Yeah....how about....this one..” he points at a small blue one, “this one seems nice....”
She looked at it "Alright!" She hummed, tails wagging a bit
With a quick swipe, he grabbed it, “so uh....now what....do we leave or?”
"Well, dont you and Veteris need one? And we also gotta pay first..."

“Ah..,,Veteris has one....just doesn’t use it a lot....but I guess I like.....this one.” He grabs a  peach colored Terreracts, “Oh, right.....payment.....yeahhh.” Sanguis dives into his waist scarf, grabbing a brown pouch.
"Its alright, I can pay! I have got alot saved up since I usually hunted for food n stuff." She hummed, smiling at him. Her tails are wagging a bit
“No, No I insist, it’s my stuff therefore I pay...” a stubborn tone in his voice, “.......who do I give the munny to.....?”
"Alright then if you so insist." She walked over to the cashier who, seemed amazed at Vulpe
He awkwardly slams the pouch full of munny on the counter “keep the change.” The man couldn’t keep eye contact with the cashier, who just just took the bag with a confused look.

Vulpe just blinked a bit. Well then...She paid for her stuff and hummed softly as she did. After getting everything all ready, she offered her hand out to Sanguis. In case he wanted to hold hands again

Sanguis quickly clutched her hand, looking down, “Mhm...” not looking up until they both left the store, “Remind me to never do that again....” he mumbled, though Vulpe could feel something wrap around one of her tails.

She nodded "Well at least we got what was needed!" She smiled, the other tails wagging still. As they start to walk she spots a dress in a store and she looks down at her current bloodstained clothes ".....Can we make a quick stop? I need some new clothing...."
“S-Sure....not too long though...” he also takes a look his less prominent blood stains, “...guess I should too.”
She nodded a bit and into the store they went!
She looked around and saw the dress that was in the window, her tails wagging. It was the pink and black one. "Heyhey, Sanguis, What do you think? Do you...think I would look good in this??"
“ʸᵒᵘ ˡᵒᵒᵏ ᵍᵒᵒᵈ ᶦⁿ ᵃⁿʸᵗʰᶦⁿᵍ, -Yeah, Ill bet you look nice in it...” he glances around the store, trying to find something he might like.

She picked up on what he said this time. Being a fox technically comes with its perks of good hearing. She blushed at his comment. "Well...Ill find some other stuff then try it all on. Ill....probably need to make extra tail holes...." she chuckled a bit
She hums as she finds other stuff to try on. Shes pretty excited...
He glances to her a few times, while picking out a few things of his own
She makes her way to the changing rooms which where pretty close. She decides to try the strawberry dress she picked out on first
“Just say my name if you need anything.”
"Alright!" She smiled at him happily before shutting the door to change
Eventually she comes back out in thr dress "What do you think?" Shes blushing a bit
Sanguis was about to say something, but then she came out, and it seemed all breath got smacked outta him, “Y-You......NICe-Nice you look, so-o nice..” compared to Vulpe he was red, very, very, red.
She blushed more "Th-Thanks....Ive....never really worn stuff like this before....I really like it..."
“Y-Yeah...well if you like it...then I like it...” he stutters out, scratching the back of his neck.
She smiled "Let me try the other stuff on as well!!!!" Shes feeling pretty good
“Cool....I might try on my stuff if that’s alright.” A small smile creeps on.
She nodded "Of course!!! I cant wait to see what you picked out." Her tails are wagging how
“A-Ah.....it’s probably not as nice as yours....” he looks down and enters the dressing room.
She tries on the butterfly dress and waits for him to come out so she can see what he looks like
“Don’t l-laugh...ok?” He said, creaking open the door and stepping out. “It’s...not much...but I thought it looked comfortable..”
"You look.....really good..." She has to hold herself back from saying he looked hot....
“Thanks....you....look really pretty too...” he hummed,
"Thank you....." She blushed "Theres....One more outfit I have yet to try on.....Ill be right back ok...?" Shes nervous
“Alright...”
She goes to change. Its her first time wearing a kinda of crop top.....she changes and then comes back out "I....really like this one....What....do you think...?"

Sanguis stared for a bit, before feeling something starting to drip from his nose, quickly his arm covers it, “GrEaT you loOK grEaT...” no his voice didn’t crack your just imagining things, he looked away, his face was so heated.
She smiled and went to go change back into her normal outfit. She was excited to be able to wear one of her new outfits when they got back to the temple!!!

The moment she left, he quickly rushed into the changing room, sure that the gloves had been already ruined by the bloodstains.....that image would be ingrained into his mind forever.....*but was that necessary a bad thing?-* 
Folding the clothes into a bag, and putting on his original clothes, and waiting for his blush to fade.....somewhat..

Vulpe had to calm her racing heart still.  Oh god he looked so good in those clothes. She nearly said he was hot outloud! Thank goodness she didnt.  Once calm she walked out and waited for him, tails wagging
He managed to stumble out looking somewhat composed, immediately grabbing her hand, “L-Lets go..” mumbling

She held his hand back. Shes pretty happy but completely unaware of whats to come.

( @Gekitoutsu Rispba  ;) )
“Vulpe.....c-can I....tell you s-something?...” oh god the nervousness is back stay calm stay calm stay fUVKIN CALM
"Yeah..!! Whats up...?" She tilted her head a bit

“I....I...” just say it just say it- “-**I think your really cool! Yeah-I really don’t know what I’ve done if I haven’t met you!**” He laughed, but on the inside, he hated himself, *you couldn’t do it, you couldn’t say it, you can’t admit how you can feel.*
**coward.**
That word kept ringing in his head, as tried to distract himself.

"I.....I wanna say something too.....Um....I....From all the timelines we've been in together...Ive.....Ive fallen for you more and more......I know it can be hard to say your feelings and Ive....wanted to confess since I first saw you as Sanguis and not just as Saké. What.....im trying to say is.....I.....I love you........" She was blushing madly "Youre just.....so...amazing..."

Sanguis stayed silent, refusing to look at her, the same words racing through his head
**Coward** **Coward** **Coward** **Coward** **Coward** **Coward** **Coward** **Coward** **Coward** **Coward** **Coward** Coward** **Coward** **Coward** **Coward** **Coward**
( its time @Gekitoutsu Rispba
Aemilius has tracked Vulpe here with her sense of smell, trying to think of a way to get rid of the kitsune.
"Sanguis....? Are....you ok....?" She tilted her head
“I-I’m.....Fine..” his demeanor seemed colder
The plasma had a few chemical smells in vials on a belt, she was ready to open them...
(Do it i have the perfect response
And then she did, a strong chemical smell filling the air.

Sanguis smelt it and started to cough
“T-The hell is that?”
"A-Alri-" Her eyes widened and she gasped. She dropped to her knees, clutching her head and covering her nose. It was too late though.
“Vu-Vulpes?!” He quickly knelt by her “H-hey! Dummy!”
Her whole body was shaking as she unwillingly shifted into her kitsune form. Her pupils had had become slits and she started to snarl.
“V-Vulpes.....?” He eyes widen, his hands shaking as he reached out to touch her.
She snapped at him, snarling still. Her eyes held a feral look. Seems the smell of the chemicals caused her to go feral.
He fell backwards, clutching his now bleeding hand, realizing that this isn’t the Vulpes he know
She took off running in a different direction. She was going after more people.
*oh hell no,* sprinting after her, he keeps yelling for everyone to keep away from the currently running rabid fox “hah......hah.....” he breathes heavy
Aemilus smiled, watching this.
She kept trying to grab someone _anyone_. She wanted to catch what she currently saw was her prey. She chased after anyone who ran away from her.
Summoning Gokuraku, he slices open a portal, leaping through it to get as close to Vulpe as possible, clutching her neck
She yelped and tried to shake him off. She let out a sort of barking noise. She wanted him _off_.
Each time she tried to shake him off, the harder he clutches, trying to keep her calm, or knock her out, or *anything*
She eventually calms down but is still growling. She might not stay calm for long.

Mindscape, he needs to go into her mindscape....but how? Panicking 
He clutches the fox’s head, then violently smashes his against her, effectively knocking himself out, and hopefully Vulpe too.
Well thats one way to do it. Shes out cold.
Vulpe is still unconscious here and there probably people standing around worried and scared

Shooting up from his nap, he immediately used Gokuraku to slice open a portal to the temple, dragging the hopefully unconscious Vulpe with him, not paying attention to the warm liquid dripping down his forehead...
Shes luckily still out cold. Shes not gonna wake up till Sanguis wakes her up

Rosearade is hanging out ontop on the roof of the store, just chilling and enjoying some sun. She sure hopes no one bugs her.

@◎☆E☆◎
Unbeknownst to her, Solum was just getting out of the store, letting out an exasperated sigh, *that was a long line*, he stretches out his wings, finally no longer cramped
Rosearade peers down at the sidewalk, noticing Solum and his wings. Her tail wagged a bit and she flew down. "Never thought I would see someone else with wings..."
His ears twitch at her approaching, wings fluffing up, which causes him to abruptly turn around, immediately on guard “Back!”
She puts her hands up in defense and took a few steps back "Sorry didnt mean to scare you."
“What do you want? Are you here to attack ms? Were you sent by the revolution?” He growled

"What??? No??? I was literally just vibing on the roof enjoying the sunlight when I noticed you had wings and that interested me. As you can see I also have wings." She stretched out of of her large dragon wings

“That is...a ridiculous reason....but I’ll except it.,” he relaxes slightly, “.....it is strange, though...that you have wings as well.” His eyes wandered to the giant leathery wing, noting it was very different compared to his small, feathery ones
"Well Im a dragon after all! Both as a human and a mun!" She showed off her dragon like tail and the scales on her arms. "Gotta have large wings so I can fly!" She hummed "Im Rosearade by the way."
